  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mouse (or gamepad) to control your character and jump as high as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some rocks are very slippery, so take your time! Grab onto them with your hammer and carefully plan your next move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=792 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb mountains and challenging levels with your trusty hammer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you fall, you lose all your progress, a true test of patience and skill!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game automatically saves your progress, allowing you to pick up exactly where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compare your best times with other players through the integrated global leaderboard!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can’t die, but every misstep serves as a reminder of your determination... or frustration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tribute to human resilience, where every fall is a new opportunity (or perhaps a reason to throw your controller across the room).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85a2b2c0c0c3ec63688ba022401337ca.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=786 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85a2b2c0c0c3ec63688ba022401337ca.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85a2b2c0c0c3ec63688ba022401337ca.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock unique skins and customizations for your cardboard box and character by completing challenges and levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/e30276ea0b057196b6cd12b7b9366a85.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/e30276ea0b057196b6cd12b7b9366a85.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/e30276ea0b057196b6cd12b7b9366a85.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Mode!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge your friends (or total strangers) in real-time! See who can climb the highest before falling spectacularly.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Leaderboard for Multiplayer.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emotes.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chat System</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/dbc6c8fe14ead1bc00d4e08977a9b7cd.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/dbc6c8fe14ead1bc00d4e08977a9b7cd.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/dbc6c8fe14ead1bc00d4e08977a9b7cd.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Notes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is a tribute to \"Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy.\"</strong> A special thanks to Bennett Foddy for the support and inspiration to create \"One Box One Goal.\" I've always wondered what \"Getting Over It\" would feel like in 3D, and this is the result!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls have been refined to perfectly suit the new 3D perspective, ensuring a smooth and immersive experience.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mouse (or gamepad) to control your character and jump as high as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some rocks are very slippery, so take your time! Grab onto them with your hammer and carefully plan your next move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.poster.avif?t=1773926808\" width=792 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.webm?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/85f22166f330bc51cc7a2b0748839da2.mp4?t=1773926808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb mountains and challenging levels with your trusty hammer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you fall, you lose all your progress, a true test of patience and skill!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game automatically saves your progress, allowing you to pick up exactly where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compare your best times with other players through the integrated global leaderboard!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can’t die, but every misstep serves as a reminder of your determination... or frustration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tribute to human resilience, where every fall is a new opportunity (or perhaps a reason to throw your controller across the room).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared